Solution
class Solution {
public:
    Solution()
      : mod(1000000007)
    { }

    /**
     * @param s: a message being encoded
     * @return: an integer
     */
    int numDecodings(string &s) {
        // write your code here

        /**
         *            i
         *      *******
         *           (i - 1)
         *  ->  ******
         *           (i - 2)
         *  ->  *****
         *
         *  dp[i]: The number of ways to decode the given substring ending at
